<div dir="ltr"><div><div><div><div>It works!!!<br></div>By putting two dash&#39;es and no equal sign, it worked fine!!<br><br>[root@host1 tmp]# mpirun --prefix /myname --host host2 /tmp/hello.out<br>Hello World from processor host2, rank 0 out of 1 processors<br>
