<div><div><br></div><div><br><div><div>On Apr 28, 2013, at 8:58 AM, E.O. &lt;<a href="mailto:ooyama.eiichi@gmail.com" target="_blank">ooyama.eiichi@gmail.com</a>&gt; wrote:</div><br><blockquote type="cite"><div dir="ltr">

